title: ADF_Collection_#2
description:
Amiga ADF-collection #2
--------------------

- Tested with WinUAE, everything should work if configuration is set
correctly.

Once again I gathered some of my favourite retro-games to one packet. Reason
why I did this was because ppl always upload horribly big packets including
nonworking adfs etc.

More retrokicks for some nerds ..
